title: Benebone Pawbler - Natural Rubber Interactive Enrichment Treat and Kibble Dispensing Dog Toy – Great for Boredom
features: YUM PUZZLE: Make your dog earn it with this challenging natural rubber enrichment toy. Just fill with their favorite treats and watch them problem-solve their way to yum-town!
EXERCISE AND ENRICH: Designed to roll unpredictably, the Pawbler loves playing hard to get. It’s sure to keep them moving as they earn their treats.
MAKE MEALTIME LAST: Let’s face it, most dogs act like jack rabbit at dinner. Slow them down with the Pawbler.
EASY TO FILL AND CLEAN: Fill in a jiffy. The bottom half is a great kibble scoop. Then unscrew and toss in the dishwasher.
HAPPINESS, GUARANTEED: Have an issue? Reach out to us directly and you’ll get a real person whose sole job is to make you and your pup happy. Shouldn't a dog enrichment toy make your dog happy?
description: Product Description Roll for rewards—fill with kibble or dry treats and watch it wobble as your clever pup hunts for treasure with the Benebone Rubber Pawbler! Made from natural rubber, this treat dispenser is great for even the toughest of pups and dishwasher safe for easy cleaning. Directions About Benebone At Benebone, we get into dog's heads... We get on their level, and create products that they would choose if they were allowed to shop for themselves. Fetch, tug, chew and treat with our new lineup of Bounce dog toys-they'll be hooked! We're Obsessed with Safety Too Keep an eye out for wear and tear. It's tough natural rubber, but it's not indestructible. Not sure if it's time to replace? Reach out to us directly and you'll get a real person whose sole job is to make you and your pup happy. What's Inside? Nothing but Natural Rubber
